---
// ItsJustIvan's Sideboard - The Kangee Edition
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ItsJustIvan's Sideboard | By a player, for the players</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,600;1,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --forest-green: #1b2e26; 
            --cream: #f4f1ea;        
            --clay: #a67c52;         
            --ink: #2c2c2c;          
            --bg: #fdfcf8;           
            --border: #e0ddd5;
            --nav-height: 70px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--ink);
            padding-top: var(--nav-height);
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-weight: 600; font-style: italic; color: var(--forest-green); margin: 0; }

        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: var(--nav-height);
            background: rgba(253, 252, 248, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .nav-title { font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
        
        .status-tag {
            font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--clay); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; margin-top: 2px;
        }
        .status-dot { height: 6px; width: 6px; background: var(--clay); border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 6px; }

        .nav-btn {
            background: var(--forest-green); color: var(--cream); padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8rem; border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .hero-slider {
            position: relative; height: 45vh; width: 100%; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }

        .slide {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-size: cover; background-position: center; opacity: 0; animation: slide-fade 12s infinite;
        }

        .slide:nth-child(1) { background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(253,252,248,0.5), rgba(253,252,248,0.5)), url('https://placehold.co/800x1200/dcd7cc/444?text=The+Vault+In+Deckbox'); animation-delay: 0s; }
        .slide:nth-child(2) { background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(253,252,248,0.5), rgba(253,252,248,0.5)), url('https://placehold.co/800x1200/c9c4b9/444?text=Custom+Lid+Details'); animation-delay: 4s; }
        .slide:nth-child(3) { background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(253,252,248,0.5), rgba(253,252,248,0.5)), url('https://placehold.co/800x1200/dcd7cc/444?text=By+A+Player'); animation-delay: 8s; }

        @keyframes slide-fade { 0% { opacity: 0; } 8% { opacity: 1; } 33% { opacity: 1; } 41% { opacity: 0; } 100% { opacity: 0; } }

        .hero-text { position: relative; z-index: 10; text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
        
        /* --- The Story Section --- */
        .story-box {
            background: #f4f1ea;
            padding: 35px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--clay);
        }

        .story-box p {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #444;
        }

        .story-box p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
        .story-quote { font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-style: italic; color: var(--forest-green); font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }

        .offering-card {
            background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .product-img { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; object-fit: cover; background: #f0f0f0; }
        .product-info { padding: 30px; }
        .product-info h3 { margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.3rem; }
        .product-info p { color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .product-info ul { padding: 0; margin: 0; list-style: none; }
        .product-info li { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.9rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; }
        .product-info li::before { content: "•"; color: var(--clay); margin-right: 12px; }

        .form-section {
            background: var(--forest-green); color: var(--cream); padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 16px; margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .form-section h2 { color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; }
        .form-section p { text-align: center; font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px; opacity: 0.9; }
        .form-group input, .form-group select, .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; font-family: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: var(--clay); color: white; padding: 16px; width: 100%; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 10px;
        }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: #999; font-size: 0.8rem; }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .offering-card { flex-direction: row; }
            .product-img { width: 40%; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; }
            .product-info { width: 60%; padding: 40px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <nav class="nav-container">
            <div class="nav-left">
                <span class="nav-title">ItsJustIvan's Sideboard</span>
                <span class="status-tag"><span class="status-dot"></span> Accepting Commissions</span>
            </div>
            <a href="#contact" class="nav-btn">Hit me up</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero-slider">
        <div class="slide"></div>
        <div class="slide"></div>
        <div class="slide"></div>
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h2>Personalized for your playstyle.</h2>
            <p style="color: #666; font-style: italic;">Built to solve the minor grievances of the game.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main class="container">
        
        <div class="story-box">
            <p>Born from a Kangee deck and the nightmare of tracking ten different flying anthems, I built these to replace the mess of dice on the table. No more fumbling, no more mental math—just stackable counters designed to fit perfectly inside your deck box.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offering-grid">
            <div class="offering-card">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/600x600/f4f1ea/1b2e26?text=The+Basic+Kit" class="product-img" />
                <div class="product-info">
                    <h3>The Basic Kit</h3>
                    <p>Stop fumbling at dice. High-contrast, stackable counters that keep your boardstate clear for everyone at the table.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Set of 12 stackable counters</li>
                        <li>High-visibility lettering for easy reading</li>
                        <li>Lightweight and portable</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="offering-card">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/600x600/f4f1ea/1b2e26?text=The+Vault" class="product-img" />
                <div class="product-info">
                    <h3>The Vault</h3>
                    <p>The total package. Organized counters in a sliding-lid case that fits perfectly inside a standard deck box.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>12-Counter Loadout</li>
                        <li>Carrying Case</li>
                        <li>Standard deck-box dimensions</li>
                        <li>Snug-fit sliding lid with standard logo</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="offering-card" style="border-color: var(--clay);">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/600x600/f4f1ea/1b2e26?text=Signature+Set" class="product-img" />
                <div class="product-info">
                    <h3>The Custom Signature</h3>
                    <p>Make it yours. We customize the counters and the lid text to match your favorite deck or inside joke.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Everything included in The Vault</li>
                        <li>Your Custom Text or Icon on the lid</li>
                        <li>Your choice of filament colors</li>
                        <li>Custom assortment of 12 counters</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section id="contact" class="form-section">
            <h2>Let's build your set</h2>
            <p>I’m just one guy with a printer, but I’d love to help you clean up your boardstate. Send me a note!</p>
            <form action="#" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>What should I call you?</label>
                    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="e.g. Urza" required />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Where can I email you?</label>
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Urza@planeswalker.com" required />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>What are you thinking for the lid / counters?</label>
                    <textarea name="message" placeholder="e.g. I want the Signature Set in Sky Blue for my Kangee deck..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>ItsJustIvan's Sideboard &copy; 2026. <br> Just a hobbyist making gear. Not affiliated with WotC.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>